│  ## Features Implemented                                                     │
│                                                                              │
│  1. **ComicGenerator** - Form to input prompts and generate comics via API   │
│  2. **ComicCard** - Display individual comics with image, status, prompt,    │
│  and actions (download, share, delete)                                       │
│  3. **ComicList** - Grid view of all comics with loading, error, and empty   │
│  states                                                                      │
│  4. **Dark Theme** - Modern glassmorphism UI design                          │
│  5. **Responsive Design** - Works on mobile and desktop                      │
│  6. **API Integration** - Connects to Go backend via Vite proxy              │
│  7. **Loading States** - Spinners and progress indicators                    │
│  8. **Error Handling** - User-friendly error messages with retry             │
│  functionality                                                               │
│  9. **Image Lazy Loading** - Progressive image loading with placeholder      │
